Name: lmtp_fuzzy_mailbox_match
Type: SWITCH
Default-Value: 0
Last-Modified: 2.3.17

If enabled, and the mailbox specified in the detail part of the recipient
(everything after the '+') does not exist, lmtpd will try to find the
closest match (ignoring case, ignoring whitespace, falling back to parent)
to the specified mailbox name.
